307
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:04,720
that's good. But don't let it worry you

308
00:10:02,399 --> 00:10:06,639
in the moment. Moving right along, my

309
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:08,880
seventh tip is to focus more on the

310
00:10:06,639 --> 00:10:10,478
