314
00:10:13,839 --> 00:10:17,519
really invested in what I'm talking

315
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:19,440
about and more specifically when I'm

316
00:10:17,519 --> 00:10:21,919
invested in the transformation I want it

317
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:23,999
to have on the audience, I don't care so

318
00:10:21,919 --> 00:10:25,678
much about the technical aspects of my

